Dolphin-specific changes (as of 2016-11-20)
-------------------------------------------

- removed all toplevel directories save msvc/ & libusb/
- removed all files save AUTHORS, Changelog, COPYING, INSTALL, NEWS,
  PORTING, README and TODO
- copied the VS project file (libusb_static_2013.vcxproj) from the msvc/
  directory to the upper directory, and modified it to insert
  dolphin-specific props
- the original config.h.in file was rewritten to make it work with CMake
  instead of configure
